<br>
The katana was designed for use with either one or two hands for the choice of use with the Wakizashi or a, yes they had them, wooden and or hide shield.  Shields were more for the common foot soldier and the rarity of refined metals made swords primarily for the elite military and the rich.<br>
<br>
I could go on, but this is an MA chat board.<br>
<br>
I think we should get one and two handed edged and blunt weapons for the MA skill.  I'd love to wield a three sectional staff.<br>
